opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 16th day of September, 2009, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the “Petition for Writ of Habeaous [sic] Corpus” is DENIED. The Prothonotary is instructed to strike the jurists’ names from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
